{"tid":917328,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日男歌手臉上黑眼圈太深！經紀人看一眼識破：你性生活太豐富","createTime":"2018-11-26T10:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T11:57:35.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"833e59f097362c9454ea729fb20afbd9edae5b89","tid":917328,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:36:09.000Z","msg":"新生代創作型歌手Tomo GO出生於日本，精通中英日粵及上海話等多種語言，不僅有語言天分，他也相當有寫歌的才華，將於30日發行全新創作專輯《商務艙Business》，不過他透露，其實專輯得來不易，因為為了發行，他滿腦子都是新歌方向、宣傳方法及預算等，讓黑眼圈爬上他的臉，不過他也笑說，以前經紀人常開玩笑說，其實他的黑眼圈是因為性生活太豐富的關係。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/25/1659361-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F1659361-XXL.jpg&h=2aa62c19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Tomo因為家庭背景，精通多國語言。<br />\n<br />\nTomo從小因為家庭背景的緣故，12歲就到上海念書3年，隨後又搬到香港繼續念書，因此不僅母語日文，就連中文以及粵語也難不倒他，他表示，就是因為在華語區待過一段時間，因此他才想用華語創作，不過也因為捨不得母語日文，因此他的創作充滿了多國語言。在新專輯裡的11首歌，就有8首是中文歌，其中5首還分別有英、日文版本。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBQ6p6y.img?h=400&amp;w=500&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBQ6p6y.img%3Fh%3D400%26w%3D500%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df&h=fd2a8b21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Tomo透露，經紀人曾說他是因為性生活太豐富，黑眼圈才那麼深。<br />\n<br />\n提到即將發行的新專輯時，Tomo則說，因為要發行專輯，所以有不少事情需要構思，腦袋也常被工作靈感塞滿，常常因此睡不好覺，導致黑眼圈跟著加深，不過他也笑說，其實之前經紀人常對他開玩笑說，他的黑眼圈重是因為「性生活太豐富」，否則應把盆菜保持在攝氏60度以上。他原本覺得不可置信，沒想到一查還真的有這種說法，所以他就靈機一動，把這個創意加入新歌《黑眼圈》中，「算是幽自己一默」。"},{"pid":"71eba0a8a721b30f072cb2a334f7e4d3543aecf6","tid":917328,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:12:31.000Z","msg":"港女歌手閪邊太黑<br />\n港男<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9900223b0fd04e49d9762705809bf83c7e215a38","tid":917328,"uid":7494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"一睇就知係邊個user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53cdf3badb2dc4310a4597c6f3ca24b36106e4e","tid":917328,"uid":196552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"盤菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0d700f6278a199ace831a33837afd38c9bf835","tid":917328,"uid":96,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:17:54.000Z","msg":"朱千雪呢"},{"pid":"1c63022ff75b3ab98e02f5a4190f27f5d84aee61","tid":917328,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"又係若無巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5103067ef9844cf88fa21f7935f7e0ec5dee5644","tid":917328,"uid":153497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:57:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">否則應把盆菜保持在攝氏60度以上。</span>"}]}